.vmoptions<br/> idea64.vmoptions</li></ol>\n<p><img alt=\"请添加图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\46439b23f1b545128436cd4fd9d61fdc.png\"/><br/> 2. <strong>打开并在最后添加如下代码</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-java\"><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Dfile<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>encoding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>UTF<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"请添加图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\74df3f39388c4fbb9b3a74e1c4aa799d.png\"/></p>\n<h2><a id=\"idea_21\"></a>第二步（打开idea）</h2>\n<ol><li><strong>对应的英文为：File——&gt;Settings——&gt;Editor——&gt;File Encodings,将三处编码格式改为UTF-8</strong></li></ol>\n<p><img alt=\"请添加图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\aa3aef8d887e453da1169c65959bcee0.png\"/><br/> <img alt=\"请添加图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\96233c1a217e468abdbaa7f4027edc02.png\"/></p>\n<ol start=\"2\"><li><strong>点击右上角下拉菜单第一个选项Edit Configurations,进入运行调试配置，找到对应的tomcat或者是application将VM options中添加上</strong><pre><code class=\"prism language-java\"><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Dfile<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>encoding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>UTF<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span>\n</code></pre> </li></ol>\n<p><img alt=\"请添加图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\77bcae94a9b2406aba6901585833a0da.png\"/></p>\n<h2><a id=\"ideahttpsimgblogcsdnimgcnaddc2f28ba81484db44559ebc8a80fdepngxossprocessimagewatermarktype_d3F5LXplbmhlaQshadow_50text_Q1NETiBAYW5fYW50ZWxvcGUsize_20color_FFFFFFt_70g_sex_16_36\"></a>第三步（关闭idea，重新打开即可）<img alt=\"请添加图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\addc2f28ba81484db44559ebc8a80fde.png\"/></h2>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Java", "cpp": 0, "csha